[msg TRL_733_1_2]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1]This allows you to confirm which attack affinities you've used on that specific enemy.[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg TRL_733_2_1]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1]When all enemies are knocked down, you will have the option to perform an All-Out Attack. This deals heavy damage to all enemies, so try and knock down enemies as often as possible.[n][uf 1 1][e]

